It has long been known that

00:21:06.200 --> 00:21:07.820
if a person is overpaid, he

00:21:07.820 --> 00:21:09.820
will most likely work worse.

00:21:11.160 --> 00:21:12.880
If a person is not paid, he will

00:21:12.880 --> 00:21:15.380
most likely leave our organization.

00:21:16.260 --> 00:21:18.880
The remuneration is merely the

00:21:18.880 --> 00:21:20.920
compensation we pay

00:21:20.920 --> 00:21:24.020
a person in a monetary or other

00:21:24.020 --> 00:21:27.400
form, as a payment for the

00:21:27.400 --> 00:21:29.440
service he provides us, for

00:21:29.440 --> 00:21:31.100
working for us and doing

00:21:31.100 --> 00:21:32.600
the actions we want from

00:21:32.600 --> 00:21:34.300
him and bringing us the

00:21:34.300 --> 00:21:38.120
results we expect from him.

00:21:38.400 --> 00:21:40.500
What is different from this motivation?

00:21:41.040 --> 00:21:46.240
Motivation is to help a person

00:21:46.240 --> 00:21:47.500
in creating such internal

00:21:47.500 --> 00:21:50.600
mechanisms that will push him

00:21:50.600 --> 00:21:52.900
to work better, to work

00:21:52.900 --> 00:21:54.120
in our company, to work on

00:21:54.120 --> 00:21:56.200
conscience, to work, as

00:21:56.480 --> 00:21:57.480
they say, with a focus

00:21:57.480 --> 00:22:00.400
to bring serious results.

00:22:00.420 --> 00:22:01.960
One of the main tools

00:22:01.960 --> 00:22:03.920
for motivating staff is

00:22:03.920 --> 00:22:05.640
feedback.

00:22:05.760 --> 00:22:08.220
In order for a person to know

00:22:08.220 --> 00:22:10.180
what is good, what is bad, how

00:22:10.180 --> 00:22:11.960
he should work, how he should

00:22:12.280 --> 00:22:13.520
not work, what he should, even

00:22:13.520 --> 00:22:15.120
learn what qualities he

00:22:15.120 --> 00:22:17.560
should develop, he needs to

00:22:17.560 --> 00:22:18.820
receive feedback.

