In the format "it's done badly,

00:22:32.000 --> 00:22:34.120
it's done wrongly", well, and

00:22:34.120 --> 00:22:35.400
as the famous joke goes,

00:22:35.400 --> 00:22:37.560
"I'd better sit at home and

00:22:37.560 --> 00:22:39.520
then I'll get a promotion,

00:22:39.520 --> 00:22:40.880
because at work I'm noticed only

00:22:40.940 --> 00:22:43.540
when I do something wrong."

